The brightness was turned down.

62
00:03:03,540 --> 00:03:06,645
These brightness buttons are a little bit fiddly,

63
00:03:06,645 --> 00:03:09,520
and it's easy to hit them by accident.

64
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:11,440
So, there you are.

65
00:03:11,440 --> 00:03:13,060
Great. Thank you.

66
00:03:13,060 --> 00:03:14,940
You're welcome.

67
00:03:14,940 --> 00:03:16,895
If we didn't ask follow up questions,

68
00:03:16,895 --> 00:03:20,965
